modification, the development, the reproduction of the Software are deemed to
be executed by experimented users and contain risks. You are responsible for
the checking by any means of fitness of the Software for your own purposes, of
checking of its working, of its Use in conditions that do not cause damages to
persons or goods.

b) The Software is provided on a « as is » basis, without warranties express or
implied other than the existence of the Software, including all disclaimer of
warranty relating to a title or deed (of property or exploitation), the lack of
infringement, the merchantability, the secured, innovative or accurate features
of the Software, the lack of mistakes, the suitability with Your equipment
and/or software configuration.



4) Disclaimer of liability
==========================

a) INRA can not be held responsible towards no one :
