5) End of contract
==================

In case of failure of the final academic user to comply with any term of this
agreement, the license will automatically terminate. In case of termination,
You must immediately destroy the software as well as any copy, adaptation,
improvement or any part of the software merged in a other software.



6) Applicable law
=================

This contract and all disputes arising out of the execution or interpretation
of this license shall be governed by French law.



7) Disputes
===========

The parties undertake to settle their differences amicably. In case of
persistent disagreement, the courts of Paris will be competent.

